QUALIFIER.NAME: Description
QUALIFIER.VALUE: Refers to the refinement of the UnitOfWorkDefinition: the trace level type. It is not required that a UnitOfWork be associated to a TraceLevelType. But if it is associated, only one Type can be specified for the Definition. In contrast, TraceLevelTypes can be reused for multiple Definitions.

QUALIFIER.NAME: Description
QUALIFIER.VALUE: The trace level type description that is implemented by the UnitOfWorkDefinition.

QUALIFIER.NAME: Description
QUALIFIER.VALUE: The UnitOfWorkDefinition which is refined by the instance of TraceLevelType.
